<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Travel Guide Generator - Error</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            color: #dc3545;
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .home-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .home-link:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Travel Guide Generator</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-container">
            <h2>Oops! Something Went Wrong</h2>
            <div class="error-message">
                <p><%= message %></p>
            </div>
            <p>Please try again later or contact support if the problem persists.</p>
            <a href="/" class="home-link">Return to Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Â© 2024 Travel Guide Generator. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>